@node not35 "TUMULT - ANNOUNCEMENT"

@{B}TUMULT@{UB} - ANNOUNCEMENT
---------------------

@{B}TUMULT@{UB}  is  an  acronym  for  "The Unoffical @{B}MUi@{UB} custom class LisT". As the name
strongly  implies  the  list  contains  information about custom classes for @{B}MUI@{UB}
(@{B}Magic  User Interface@{UB}). Among other things the information on the list includes
the  email-address  of  the  author, a link to a support page if available and a
short description of each class.

There  are several reasons for the creation of @{B}TUMULT@{UB}. One of the most important
reasons  is  that  it  has  always  been  a problem for normal users to find the
classes  they  need.  Not  all  classes  are on @{B}Aminet@{UB} and often the archives on
@{B}Aminet@{UB}  are  not the latest releases. @{B}TUMULT@{UB} will also be an easy way for custom
class  authors to see whether or not they are in the process of re-inventing the
wheel. This is why unfinished classes are needed on the list too.

The  list  is  completely  non-commercial.  It is also independent of the normal
@{B}MCC@{UB}-registration  service,  and  can therefore not be considered official in any
way.  All  classes  can  be  on  the  list.  They  can be officially registered,
unregistered,  candidates  or anything else. They don't even have to be released
yet to be on the list.

You can find the list at the following URL:
@{B}www.amiga.dk/tumult/@{UB}

If  you  have any questions about the list then you can write to @{I}floyd@amiga.dk@{UI}.
If  you  want  to  register  one  of  your  own  classes  then  you can find the
registration procedure (and a template) at the homepage.
